import { Card, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Cards = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container sx={{background:'#FFFFED', display:''}}>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Typography>
                This is the card.
            </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
            <Card sx={{height:'50px'}}>
                Hello
            </Card>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}

export default Cards
